---
import Container from "@components/container.astro";
import Layout from "@layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Acknowledgements">
  <Container>
    <h1 class="text-center text-2xl text-gray-500 font-extrabold pt-6">Acknowledgements</h1>
    <p>
      Building and maintaining Giorgiosaud.io has been a journey of learning, collaboration, and creativity. This platform is more than just a notebook; it’s a reflection of the knowledge, experiences, and inspiration I’ve gained from countless sources. I’d like to take a moment to express my gratitude to the people and communities that have made this possible.
    </p>   
    <h2>To My Family </h2>
    
    <p>   
      To my wife and children, your unwavering support and patience fuel everything I do. You remind me every day of why I strive to grow and share knowledge.
    </p>
    
    <h2>To the Developer Community</h2>
    
    <p>
      This site wouldn’t exist without the incredible global community of developers who share their expertise, solve problems collaboratively, and inspire innovation. Platforms like GitHub, Stack Overflow, and developer blogs have been invaluable resources throughout my career.
    </p>
    
    <h2>To My Colleagues and Mentors</h2>
    
    <p>
      To my colleagues at Modyo and beyond, thank you for challenging me to think differently and for the collaborations that have expanded my skill set. To my mentors over the years, your guidance has been instrumental in shaping my perspective and approach to software development.
    </p>
    <h2>To My Readers</h2>
    
    <p>
      Whether you’re here to learn, solve a specific problem, or just explore, thank you for visiting. Your curiosity and feedback keep this project alive and evolving.
    </p>
    <h2>Tools and Technologies</h2>
    
    <p>
      This platform wouldn’t be possible without the amazing open-source tools and frameworks used in its creation, including:
      <ul>
        <li>
          Astro – for powering this site’s modern, performant design.
        </li>
        <li>
          Tailwind CSS – for styling and layout.
        </li>
        <li>
          Markdown and VS Code – for creating and organizing content.
        </li>
        <li>
          GitHub – for version control and collaboration.
        </li>
        <li>
          Vercel – for seamless deployment and hosting.
        </li>
        <li>
          Cloudflare – for fast, secure, and reliable content delivery.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </p>
    <h2>Special Thanks</h2>
    
    <p>
      A heartfelt thanks to everyone who has directly or indirectly supported this project. From family and friends to professional connections, your encouragement has been invaluable.
    </p>
    
    <p>
      This is just the beginning of a journey that I hope will benefit developers at every level. Let’s keep building, learning, and sharing together.
    </p>
  </Container>
</Layout>
<style>
  h2{
    @apply text-balance text-center text-2xl font-bold py-6
  }
  *{
    @apply text-gray-500
  }
  p{
    @apply text-gray-500 text-pretty
  }
</style>